-to-day is completely different. You'll be given 1 client to start. You'll be briefed on the client, the goals, the campaigns. You'll be expected to come up with and pitch 'Tests'. A test may be 'Automating Twitter by mentioning influencers in our skyscraper content'. Assigning a budget and Pareto rating (Basically, is this 80/20, is this the highest impact thing I can be doing right now, for my time). You'll then be expected to execute, report, scaling winners and dousing failures. As one of our Growth Mercenaries, you'll be expected to build your own personal brand as a thought leader. Writing content, helping us with internal projects such as Youtube. You'll be expected to travel to conferences, to network, to build up your repertoire in both Crypto and Marketing. And of course, you need to be constantly absorbing, learning, bringing in new ideas from the most random of sources. Constantly being on the forefront and pushing the boundaries of what Marketing will be in tomorrow's world. We're mainly looking for Full-Time commitments, however, we're open to contractors. What we offer you: Competitive salary tied to the $, given in Crypto. Either on a monthly or contract basis. Budget, tools, bonuses, conferences, Iron-Sharpens-Iron Team. Huge autonomy, as-much-resources as you need, invites to our events around the world to network and meet world leaders, the possibility to grow yourself into your best possible you. How to apply: Apply with a 1-pager Case study of your favourite Growth Campaign you've run for a client (Or yourself). Accompanied by 1 or 2 paragraphs about yourself. Please also write your specialisms ('m in the top 1% at {{Analytics}}, {{SEO}}, {{Instragram Growth}}, {{Influencer Marketing}} etc.... FInally, include where you want to be in 8760 hours time (1 year). What habits do you want to be doing (Meditation, working out), where do you want to be professionally (Speaking at conferences, podcasts, a thought leader on X). Skills Project Management, 